Alaska Guard Assists Juneau Following Glacial Flooding

JOINT BASE ELMENDORF-RICHARDSON, Alaska - The Alaska National Guard activated Juneau Guardsmen Aug. 7 to assist with recovery and cleanup following recent flooding after the Mendenhall Glacier’s Suicide Basin released.Gov.
